            <title>[LU-8523] sanity test_311: objs not destroyed after unlink</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8523</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Saurabh Tandan &amp;lt;saurabh.tandan@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/7359c424-6700-11e6-906c-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/7359c424-6700-11e6-906c-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_311 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
