                            <comment id="163504" author="adilger" created="Tue, 30 Aug 2016 00:45:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch landed to master. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please remember that patches which only affect tests can use&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;Test-Parameters: trivial&lt;/tt&gt;, and if it is some test other than &lt;tt&gt;sanity&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;lnet-selftest&lt;/tt&gt; then it should also include &lt;tt&gt;testlist=modified_test_name&lt;/tt&gt; to test the modified test script. That reduces testing time, as well as reducing the risk of hitting unrelated test failures. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
